PyMetric 0.8 (20091014)

  * Add GPLv2 licence
  * Custom colormap for edges when showing load
  * Suppress edge label when metric equals default metric,
    and add 'all-metrics' option to override when plotting.
  * Fix bug when we only have linkload data in one direction
    for a link.
  * Add a with-transit option to the 'linkinfo' command, showing
    which (start,end) node-pairs use the link as a transit link.
  * Port code to the new 1.00 NetworkX API.

PyMetric 0.7 (20090716)
  
  * Show link utilizations in prompt
  * Fix bug with changing allready changed metrics
  * Fix bug with resetting anycast nodes when
    simulation ends
  * Add configuration file option and sample
  * Add sample startup script

PyMetric 0.5.1 (20090602)

  * Bugfix for load distribution

PyMetric 0.5 (20090529)

  * Add linkload/capacity stuff.
  * Add linkinfo command.
  * Add timeout to rerouting (2 minutes)
  * Add options to change command
  * More documentation
  * Various bugfixes

PyMetric 0.4.1 (20090515)

  * Bugfix for broken simpath/diffpath

PyMetric 0.4 (20090515)

  * More sensible reroute command
  * Add anycast simulation
  * Various cleanups and bugfixes

PyMetric <= 0.3 (20090513)

  * No detailed changelog kept

